data.description: HIGHLY MOTIVATED SELLERS! Cute 2 bedroom / 2 bath home with FENCED backyard, and NEW ROOF IN 2021!!! Central water, tile floors throughout the home. Home has 1 car carport and VERY LARGE driveway to park up to 4 cars. Close to shopping, restaurants, etc. No Homeowner's Fees or Restrictions. MORTGAGE IS ASSUMABLE, RATE IS 3.25% SELLER WILL HELP WITH CLOSING COST..
